{
  "stem": "18770.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 379.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They all went back after making some money and they were all killed by Hitler.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I didn't, I didn't-- I don't, you know, I don't remember--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just stories about them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the Lax family, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, my mother's family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do have some memories, but they're, again, a very young child's memory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm five years old or six years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] being brought into room, probably to say goodnight to my parents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think that was the, you know, the way it was done-- especially if there was company.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where we would be put in our pajamas and then we would come in and, you know, say good night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember coming in the room, and my parents and some of my uncles and aunts, sitting around listening to shortwave radio and hearing this rather angry or strange-sounding German voice-- which I only realized in retrospect later-- years later when I discussed it with my sister and my mother-- was Hitler.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they were listening to Hitler giving one of his speeches that was being broadcast.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was definitely a feeling of tension in the room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't remember ongoing discussions about it, but I do remember that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know there were family discussions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember whether I ever had any sense of those directly or because I know about them because I was told about them later on-- those two things tend to fuse, you know, together.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You don't know what's recovered memory and what's just remembered anecdotes.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
